Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got in the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了他递给我的下药的汽水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}drank the drugged soda he gave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就失去意识了  醒来发现在他家地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}passed out, and woke up in his basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对警察也是这样的说法  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's what you relayed to the police, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天在这里也是同样的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's what you maintain here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在已经宣誓的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}under sworn oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人  我有一份一页的文档\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your Honor, I have a one-page document
