Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以递给证人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I approach the witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对  法官大人  未在证据发现阶段公布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Objection, Your Honor, this was not disclosed in discovery.
