Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃利斯小姐  你手上拿的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Wallis, what is it that you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一份打印的两个账号之间的聊天记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A printed chat log between two screen names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你念一下账户名吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you please state those screen names?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布伦奈斯4和特劳玛拉玛79\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berenice4 and Traumarama79.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃利斯小姐  能否请你念出高亮段落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Wallis, could you please read the highlighted passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃利斯小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Wallis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"特劳玛拉玛79"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Traumarama79."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我到马丁家里寻找安全感"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I went to Martin's looking for safety."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"要是知道我是自愿前往  人们会怎么想"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"What would people think if they knew I went there willingly?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"他们会怀疑整件事的真实性"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"It'd make them question my whole story."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你记得发生过这样的对话吗  沃利斯小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you recall this conversation, Ms. Wallis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是应该叫你特劳玛拉玛79\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or should I call you Traumarama79?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的网名  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is your screen name, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些聊天内容是隐私\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those chats were private.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们监听了我们的电话吗  这合法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did they tap our phones? Can they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查了查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did some digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你姐姐一直以网名"布伦奈斯4"的名义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It appears that your sister has been chatting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}under the screen name "Berenice4."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父母在给她打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your parents are calling her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布伦奈斯就是艾希莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berenice is Ashley?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有对我说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You haven't been honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们的案子是很大的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a huge blow to our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你还有什么瞒着我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there is anything else you're not telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的所作所为无法用语言弥补\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no apologizing for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不该喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't have been drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该开车载你  却偏偏载了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't have given you a ride, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对发生的一切负全部责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I take full responsibility for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错  杰米  你可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's great, Jamie. You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但文斯·富勒什么也没做错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Vince Fuller didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}布伦奈斯4  "凯特  抱歉让你以这样的方式发现真相"\N布伦奈斯4"我想让你有人可以谈谈心"\N布伦奈斯4"但现实中你从来不和我说话"\N布伦奈斯4"给我打电话  拜托了"\N特劳玛拉玛79  "你怎么能这么对我"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾希莉就是布伦奈斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ashley is Berenice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的败了  玛洛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm bugging out, Mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说原因了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she say why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了  还用这种完全站不住脚的借口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and she had this weak-ass excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我需要有人谈心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of, "I needed someone to talk to."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒挺贴心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sounds... nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我找到了同类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I had found someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了地狱般的生活存活下来的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who had been through hell and back and survived it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为在和未来的我聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought that I was chatting with my future,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果她根本不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she doesn't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的全貌还是拼不完整\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have the whole puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没料到布伦奈斯的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wrong about Berenice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也记不起安娜贝尔是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I don't remember Anabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我知道的根本不是全貌呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if I don't have all the pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试西尔维亚的办法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to try what Sylvia suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没有开门  请稍后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're actually not open yet if you wanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在说这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you saying this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰米让我想了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jamie got me thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在惩罚错的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About how... I've been punishing the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我很想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到也没有多开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't even enjoy hearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做错什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did I do that was so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我男朋友受伤的时候陪在他身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be there for my boyfriend when he got hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太敏感了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, everyone was staring and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候你决定替我们两个出柜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that's when you tried to out us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一刻除了我们两个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't thinking about anyone else in that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有心思去想别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}except for you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕极了  文斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was terrified, Vince.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我不怕吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I'm not scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑人  还是同性恋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm black. And gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身处德克萨斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一起面对这一切的  本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were in this together, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果你把我弃如敝履\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just tossed me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用现在就答复我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to answer me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想重新赢得你的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I want to earn your trust back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you'll let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想在这里见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really wanted to meet me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有那么多地方可以去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是真相埋藏的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is where the truth lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个都想要真相  对吗  珍妮特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's what we both want, right, Jeanette?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从去年夏天起我就想和你一起面对真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've wanted to face the truth with you since last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么现在想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我家手里赢走1100万伤害不到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Taking $11 million from my family won't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但会让我父母一贫如洗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it will completely bankrupt my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你看我要赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So now that you think I might win,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然愿意庭外和解了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're interested in settling this outside of court?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤天害理的事你没少干  珍妮特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've done some dirty shit, Jeanette,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但把聊天记录当庭甩在我脸上太没品了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but springing those chat logs on me in court was a low blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电视上公开我的名字才低劣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Naming me on TV was a low blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷走了我的创伤日记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stole what was basically my trauma journal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并在法庭上公开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and shared it in a courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不出来这有多残忍吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you not see how cruel that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不出自己毁了我的生活吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you not see that you ruined my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你偷走了我的  -反正你也不想要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You stole mine! - You didn't even want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了好多好多页\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have read pages and pages
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和布伦奈斯的对话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of your chat with Berenice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不知道整个故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I don't know the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道你很幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I know that you're lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丁·哈里斯确实有不可告人的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that there are some serious secrets buried with Martin Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莫莉·格林  站在斯凯林法院的前方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Molly Green, standing on the steps of Skylin Courthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮特·特纳和凯特·沃利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where Jeanette Turner and Kate Wallis
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特纳诉沃利斯一案的第三天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have both yet to appear on day three
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,均尚未出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Turner v. Wallis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件的更多真相正浮出水面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More on this story as it unfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你说我偷了你的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since you're accusing me of stealing your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那杰米呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what about Jamie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在失踪前就跟他分手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were over him before you went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当你回来后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when you came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却依然夺走了他  即使你知道我爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you reclaimed him anyway, even though I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  那是因为你不遗余力地把我留在地狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you went to great sick lengths to leave me in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让自己拥有他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in order to keep him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我没有  -那我们直说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't. - Let's get to it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么可隐瞒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have anything to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你闯入过这栋房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you broke into this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  为了玩捉迷藏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. To play hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是秘密  我去年就告诉警察了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's no secret. I told the cops that last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, not that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在93年平安夜又进来过一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you did it again on Christmas Eve in '93.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我那天没有去地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I didn't go into the basement that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果你知道  那我猜你也没有在地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if you know that, then I guess you weren't in the basement, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对  我不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们还真是坦诚相待了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we're really being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是  我知道你看到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am. I know you saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我没看到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I know I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闯入的那夜  我一个人在家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The night you broke in, I was home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我会任由你这个红发小鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I'd let a funny little redhead like you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处乱跑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}run around loose here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉  我必须要拥有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Julia, I've got to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我在玩...  -雪球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And I was messing with... - The snow globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在打电话  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were making a phone call, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰米在答录机上收到了一通奇怪的留言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jamie got this weird message on his answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得可能是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We thought it might be you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根本说不通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, I mean, it didn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被绑架了怎么还能打电话呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could you have been making a phone call while you were kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是杰米的私人电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've reached Jamie's private line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言莫名其妙  只有呼吸声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The message was nonsense. It was breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我听到那个跑调的雪球后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once I heard that out-of-tune snow globe,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是你从楼上打的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew you called from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到死亡把我们分离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Till death do us part.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见我的那晚  我藏在二楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The night you saw me, I hid on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确定没人在家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was sure no one was home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在商场看到了马丁·哈里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw Martin Harris at the mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我听到了一个声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then I heard a noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿上雪球后就走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took the snow globe and I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了你的项链\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found your necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}加油姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果项链能证明什么  我早就被捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the necklace proved anything, I'd be arrested by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难道不知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我往窗外一看  看到了你的自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I looked out this window and I saw your bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你没看到我的脸  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you didn't see my face, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了你的声音  我找到了你的项链\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard your voice, I found your necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你的自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I saw your bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没跟你对视吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About holding eye contact, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸在外被阴影遮住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your face was shadowed outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你朝着我  我看到了你的自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you were facing me and I saw your bike
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮子上还有愚蠢的卡片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the stupid card on the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, that's my bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谁在乎  -快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who cares? - Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有手提音响的自行车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bike with the boombox?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊  我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, we have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有卡片吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the card?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的自行车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛洛丽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Mallory's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛洛丽看见了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mallory's the one who saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛洛丽吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was Mallory?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的  你这回肯定要被抓了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit. You are so getting busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛洛丽之后告诉我说她看见我闯进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mallory told me later she saw me broke in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她希望我能被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was hoping to see me get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定等到了我离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She must have waited until I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她决定跟踪我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then she decided to follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时你看到了玛洛丽  以为是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That must be when you saw Mallory and you thought it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这次又偷了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you steal this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -你因为清单的事对我说教\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - You lectured me about the list,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有违禁品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about the contraband.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表现得比我道德高尚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You played holier-than-thou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你不再跟我做朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right up until cutting me off as a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你一直以来都在偷偷溜进那房子里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you've been sneaking into that house this entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我...  -你那么做肯定感觉很爽  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I, um... - You get some sort of sick pleasure out of it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信你还没被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe you haven't gotten caught yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个伪君子  而且说真的还是个怪胎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a hypocrite and honestly a real weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是怪胎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  如果你这么在乎  拿走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, if you care so much, just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不是朋友了  你为什么在乎我干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not even friends anymore, why do you care what I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走这愚蠢的东西  赶紧走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So just take the stupid thing and get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把雪球给了玛洛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave Mallory the snow globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不肯还给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wouldn't give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是为保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.26,0:23:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜搜她的房间  你肯定能找到雪景球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you search her room, I'm sure you'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是玛洛丽看到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was really Mallory that saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时  如果知道我搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I didn't think I was right,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.75,0:23:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不会指控你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have never accused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮特  我太对不起你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeanette, I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能问一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你俩在这屋里都发生什么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what happened between you two in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.53,0:24:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和马丁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.54,0:24:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martin and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.04,0:24:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.67,0:24:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他友善  富有魅力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}kind and fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.06,0:24:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知如何形容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really know how else to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.82,0:24:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他似乎  -像是有很多秘密的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He seemed... - Like someone who had secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.03,0:24:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.58,0:25:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这过了一夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I slept over that first night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.44,0:25:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚过后  我就住下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That night led to more nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.25,0:25:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他也不仅是友情了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And friends led to more than friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.50,0:25:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们曾经\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two were...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.40,0:25:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来事情变得很黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things escalated to a really dark place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.97,0:25:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有件事  我想不起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's just one thing that I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.36,0:25:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理医生告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my therapist says that...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.35,0:25:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我回到那下面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I go back down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.86,0:25:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有助于我想起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that maybe it will help unlock the memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.93,0:25:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地下室吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Down to the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.86,0:25:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要和我一起吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.79,0:25:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.37,0:26:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.78,0:27:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我获救的那晚  他到地下室来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The night before I was rescued, he came down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.75,0:27:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.48,0:27:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些不对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.14,0:27:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很憔悴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was vulnerable
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.31,0:27:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎又平静得不对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but weirdly seemed at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.50,0:27:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来他好像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seemed like he had...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.22,0:27:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出了什么决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.09,0:27:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时以为  他鼓足勇气要杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought he had worked up the courage to actually kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.84,0:27:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经你问一切将如何结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You asked me once how this ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.60,0:27:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试过想其他办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've tried to find another way,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.84,0:27:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but there isn't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.18,0:27:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.52,0:28:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会想到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.80,0:28:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.62,0:28:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天警察来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The police came here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.03,0:28:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They did?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.71,0:28:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们拿着搜查令回来这儿取证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.65,0:28:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是时间问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before they're back with a search warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.92,0:28:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是安娜贝尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Anabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.70,0:28:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是传家宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a family heirloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.04,0:28:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要把她带下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you bring her down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.77,0:28:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她夺走了我父亲的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She took my father's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.13,0:29:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用她取我性命吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna take mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.35,0:29:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为我做过的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry for the things I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.02,0:29:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及接下来要做的事  感到抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what I'm about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.20,0:29:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  马丁  不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martin, please, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.28,0:29:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.25,0:29:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去过你的生活吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go live your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.58,0:29:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看我们曾经畅想的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See the world like we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.17,0:29:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得我曾深深爱过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And know that you were truly loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.18,0:29:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了  凯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.66,0:30:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.03,0:30:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.13,0:30:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.16,0:30:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.78,0:30:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你我之间的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.16,0:31:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会找到办法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.64,0:31:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪给我  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just give me the gun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.51,0:31:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想要这么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't wanna do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.17,0:31:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.48,0:32:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整夜  我都守着他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sat with him all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.94,0:32:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我内心乱作一团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.91,0:32:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And guilty for loving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.33,0:32:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的恨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And for hating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.45,0:32:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还为杀死他而悔恨不已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.56,0:32:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了早上  我报了警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the morning, I called the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.35,0:32:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可新闻报道他和警方交火而身亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The news said he died in a shootout.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.20,0:33:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为他死于枪伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They assumed that, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.81,0:33:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有这样的猜测报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he died of a gunshot wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.50,0:33:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.03,0:33:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.20,0:33:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久后  我可能也用外界的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I might have internalized that, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.66,0:33:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说服了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.66,0:33:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心理医生说  这事有可能发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My therapist says that can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.55,0:33:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是那个坏人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.35,0:33:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.65,0:33:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.94,0:33:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  没人会责怪你杀了马丁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, no one could blame you for killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.37,0:33:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮特  你应该告我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeanette, you should sue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.89,0:33:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该遭受这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't deserve any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.44,0:33:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  拿走赔偿金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should go, take the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.61,0:33:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压根就不是赔偿金的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was never about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.68,0:33:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what was it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.56,0:33:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自始至终\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I ever wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.52,0:34:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was to just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.40,0:34:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想体验下你过的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}maybe feel what it was like
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.00,0:34:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说我要变成你  就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to actually be you, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.64,0:34:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没感到过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never felt like I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.50,0:34:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人欢迎  或是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}popular or...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.62,0:34:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽动人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.42,0:34:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心满意足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.45,0:34:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想知道那都是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to know what that felt like.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.32,0:34:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.37,0:34:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沐浴在阳光下的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have the sun shining on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.19,0:34:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我被绑架过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.14,0:34:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.10,0:34:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和珍妮特·特纳深入交谈后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After speaking to her in depth myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.10,0:34:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一事  我万分确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there is another truth that I am 100% certain of.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.07,0:34:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮特·特纳没在马丁·哈里斯家中看见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeanette Turner did not see me in Martin Harris's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.84,0:35:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是媒体所报道的恶人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is not the monster the media has made her out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.09,0:35:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮特·特纳是一名受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeanette Turner is a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.41,0:35:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特  所以说你撒谎了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kate, does that make you a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.31,0:35:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污蔑一名无辜女孩  你作何感想呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you feel dragging an innocent girl's name through the mud?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.35,0:35:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特  是什么促使你这样做呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What prompted this, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.92,0:35:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去哪儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.27,0:35:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛洛丽  我知道你看到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mal, I know you saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.86,0:35:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我做朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You befriended me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.48,0:35:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对你看见我这事  只字不提\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And didn't say a word to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.13,0:35:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.86,0:35:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两件事怎么能共存呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are both of those things true?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.34,0:35:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我个解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I deserve an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.48,0:35:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.87,0:36:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  玛洛丽  对我掩饰什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Mal, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.57,0:36:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到一名女子行动自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw a woman living freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.21,0:36:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被关在地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.92,0:36:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是马丁·哈里斯的女友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I figured it was Martin Harris's girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.73,0:36:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是姐妹  或是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or... sister or...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.69,0:36:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.11,0:36:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对了一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were half-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.42,0:36:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一名失踪的女孩在别人家客厅打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It-it didn't make sense for a missing girl
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.87,0:36:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时觉得这说不通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be in the living room making a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.47,0:36:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那时候看见我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's when you saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.60,0:36:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我压根想不到  那会是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never in a million years imagined that it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.32,0:36:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.80,0:36:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从新闻上得知你获救前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't really think much of it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.12,0:37:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没多想过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until I heard about your rescue on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.92,0:37:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑匪在激烈的交火中  中枪身亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And her abductor has been killed in a deadly shootout.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.12,0:37:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的新闻小组就在现场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our news team was there on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.16,0:37:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件出现了惊人  可怕的转折\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in a shocking and disturbing turn of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.31,0:37:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}少女凯特·沃利斯获救
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.22,0:37:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特·沃利斯指控马丁·哈里斯为绑架者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kate Wallis's alleged kidnappr was Martin Harris,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.89,0:37:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丁·哈里斯曾是斯凯林高中助理校长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who was the assistant principl at Skylin High School in Texa.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.97,0:37:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且所有人都认为你被关在地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the world only thought you were ever in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.97,0:37:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说出秘密就等于拆穿了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Telling my secret meant telling yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.33,0:37:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我思前想后  觉得这与我无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I chalked it up to being none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.16,0:37:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.51,0:37:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们成了朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then we became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.03,0:37:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.22,0:37:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真没劲啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boo, you're no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.41,0:38:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.04,0:38:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要坦诚相待吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to "No more secrets"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就坐长途汽车  离开镇子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna hop a Greyhound and get out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.71,0:38:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不会出现在你面前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will never see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.06,0:38:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我丢在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.72,0:38:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.55,0:38:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我而去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.75,0:38:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.86,0:38:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片场保持安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quiet on set.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.86,0:38:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}一个月后
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.65,0:38:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.55,0:38:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.95,0:38:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在我身边的是珍妮特·特纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sitting here with Jeanette Turner,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.95,0:38:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位姑娘曾被深深地误解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the young woman at the center of a misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.51,0:38:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年来  她的生活和内心都备受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that cost a year of her life and her sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.95,0:39:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is, in this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.73,0:39:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是全美最冤屈的女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the most wronged woman in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.95,0:39:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeanette...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.70,0:39:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坚韧不拔  通情达理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}given your resilience, your grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.91,0:39:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顽强不屈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.36,0:39:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事迹鼓舞人心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you are an inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.13,0:39:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你造成的误解  也有我的过失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And for the part I played in what happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.38,0:39:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深感抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.85,0:39:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  玛莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Marsha.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.36,0:39:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日在此受访  我倍感荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm incredibly grateful to be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.91,0:39:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾观看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've watched and...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.96,0:39:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你现在满心都是和谐与宽容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you're all kumbaya and forgiveness now,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.50,0:39:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.01,0:39:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就是在看一个彻头彻尾的怪胎秀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what I'm watching is an absolute creep show.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.31,0:39:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.33,0:39:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不巧这是个无辜的怪胎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that creep also happens to be innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.05,0:39:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开车兜风去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go for a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.93,0:39:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说我从这一切中学到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...if there's one thing I've learned from all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.37,0:39:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们去哪  -我不得不问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where are we going? - I have to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.87,0:39:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终止了对凯特的诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You dropped the lawsuit against Kate,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.48,0:39:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃了近在咫尺的1100万调解金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}walking away from a potential $11 million settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.59,0:40:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What made you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.98,0:40:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莎  这压根就不是钱的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was never about the money, Marsha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.57,0:40:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有真相才重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.52,0:40:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在真相大白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now that the truth has come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.97,0:40:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今  你的生活过得怎样呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what does life look like on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.33,0:40:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有最好的爸爸  他一直支持我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I have the greatest dad who never left my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.73,0:40:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我梦寐以求的完美男友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and... the best boyfriend I could hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.93,0:40:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,访谈结束前  你还有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything else you'd like to share
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.35,0:40:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before you wrap up?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.60,0:40:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个曾经在此对我指名道姓的女生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is something I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.07,0:40:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想对你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the girl who named me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.95,0:40:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本可以早日澄清事件  但你没那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who could have cleared all this up sooner but didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.28,0:40:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特·沃利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kate Wallis...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.76,0:40:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原谅你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.30,0:40:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.07,0:41:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱这首歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.76,0:41:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你得和我下车一起跳舞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are getting out and dancing with me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.60,0:41:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀  好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.83,0:41:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.75,0:42:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.51,0:42:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.73,0:42:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是马丁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.34,0:42:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.64,0:42:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到我的话  我是凯特·沃利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If anyone can hear me, it's Kate Wallis!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.57,0:42:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.38,0:43:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丁把我关在下面了  请救救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martin's locked me down here. Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.71,0:43:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救我出去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please help me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.57,0:43:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is anybody there?


